replies.bodyText:
@oowekyala I've added a simple test case for var and it seems to work as long as the initializer expression is not a method call. But I think, the lack of resolving method call result types is part of PMD 6. Maybe you fixed this already on the 7 branch?
Anyway: The goal of this PR was to fix the NPE, it was never a goal to improve the rule.
Feel free to create a new issue for tracking the false negative with the above sample.

